Package: com.joshuaseltzer.noautodisablelpm
Name: NoAutoDisableLPM
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Prevents the system from automatically disabling Low Power Mode when the battery reaches 80%. Tested on iOS 15 (should work up to at least iOS 17). Research and investigation credit goes to @PoomSmart.
Maintainer: Joshua Seltzer <joshua.seltzer90@gmail.com>
Author: Joshua Seltzer <joshua.seltzer90@gmail.com>
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate (>= 0.9.5000), firmware (>=15.0)
